   <mods:abstract>Maria, Ann and William in Rye for ten days; she is alone with little
            Sarah. Johnny Lyon will probably want a considerable sum but has not named it yet. The
            mill is raised and almost covered -- will be beneficial to the country and profitable to
            you. Fears death of Mrs. Lyons will set back affairs of the farm. Mr. Grant√Üs business
            not yet settled. Will enclose news from the Minerva from the 6th that may be
            useful.</mods:abstract>
